rquitectura geral\n- supervisor canónico\n- contracts principais\n- operators alinhados\n- deterministic substrate muito mais coeso\n- limpeza conceptual do runtime\n- esqueleto do supervisor runtime canónico criado\n- pesquisa\n\nSource: memory/2026-03-31.md#L250-L289","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-03-31.md#L250-L289"}],"provider":"openai","model":"text-embedding-3-small","citations":"auto","mode":"hybrid"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775035710884}}
