ode is direct_select, so no fallback selection was used.\\\"],\\\"key_errors\\\":[\\\"No PUB/config/runtime evidence was available here to validate that account 003 and language fr are a structurally valid target.\\\",\\\"Job construction and blocking validation could not be completed, so VO handoff is not ready.\\\"],\\\"reasoning\\\":\\\"I read the PM supervisor, handoff, and implementation-status contracts. direct_select permits only the requested target and forbids silent substitution, but this session did not provide the operational PUB/config artifacts needed to confirm the target or build a validated PM job. I therefore treated the request as an explicit direct target with unresolved validation, not as a successful handoff.\\\"}\",\n      \"mediaUrl\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"durationMs\": 14206,\n    \"agentMeta\": {\n      \"sessionId\": \"badf6170-2c34-4550-aa28-a98d2f182c20\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input\": 4083,\n        \"output\": 583,\n        \"cacheRead\": 17920,\n        \"total\": 12959\n      },\n      \"lastCallUsage\": {\n        \"input\": 3393,\n        \"output\": 350,\n        \"cacheRead\": 9216,\n        \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n        \"total\": 12959\n      },\n      \"promptTokens\": 12609\n    },\n    \"aborted\": false,\n    \"systemPromptReport\": {\n      \"source\": \"run\",\n      \"generatedAt\": 1775050595095,\n      \"sessionId\": \"badf6170-2c34-4550-aa28-a98d2f182c20\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:sm_pm_production_manager:main\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n      \"workspaceDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_pm_production_manager\",\n      \"bootstrapMaxChars\": 20000,\n      \"bootstrapTotalMaxChars\": 150000,\n      \"bootstrapTruncation\": {\n        \"warningMode\": \"once\",\n        \"warningShown\": false,\n        \"truncatedFiles\": 0,\n        