{"type":"message","id":"07e6e5f0","parentId":"6ee30de6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:58:47.179Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qfuAlZQFYdGDYGY7EEbRkMZ4|fc_0785557c08065f410169cd4ec30f0c8190bb4b8df2cbfa7715","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\implementation\\s1\\S1_IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md","oldText":"### Current runtime shape\nThe runtime currently performs, in canonical form:\n1. preflight validation\n2. path resolution\n3. batch planning\n4. payload creation for operators\n5. operator invocation\n6. batch validation\n7. merge\n8. whole-artifact validation\n9. scene bible generation\n10. checkpoint writing\n11. structured result summarization\n","newText":"### Current runtime shape\nThe runtime currently performs, in canonical form:\n1. preflight validation\n2. path resolution\n3. batch planning\n4. payload creation for operators\n5. operator invocation\n6. deterministic normalization where needed\n7. batch validation\n8. merge\n9. whole-artifact validation\n10. scene bible generation\n11. checkpoint writing\n12. structured result summarization\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\docs\\\\implementation\\\\s1\\\\S1_IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md\",\"oldText\":\"### Current runtime shape\\nThe runtime currently performs, in canonical form:\\n1. preflight validation\\n2. path resolution\\n3. batch planning\\n4. payload creation for operators\\n5. operator invocation\\n6. batch validation\\n7. merge\\n8. whole-artifact validation\\n9. scene bible generation\\n10. checkpoint writing\\n11. structured result summarization\\n\",\"newText\":\"### Current runtime shape\\nThe runtime currently performs, in canonical form:\\n1. preflight validation\\n2. path resolution\\n3. batch planning\\n4. payload creation for operators\\n5. operator invocation\\n6. deterministic normalization where needed\\n